summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 3549 , for the improvement of 14th Avenue West, from West Ray Street to the north margin of West Barrett Street; by grading and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 43866, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
